Project Description

This project's aim is to design, develop and -hopefully- provide the general public with a complete and comprehensible service to promote, participate and organise carpooling. 

More information can be found here: 
http://hackerspace.gr/wiki/CarPooling

If you want to help out, you can join on the dev mailing list:
http://groups.google.com/group/oscp-dev

If you just want to see the pool of ideas and specifications on the project, you can visit (and contribute) on the etherpad:
http://pad.hackerspace.gr/p/CarPooling


